{{fr-intj}}

# [[yes]] {{qualifier|used to contradict a negative statement}}
#: {{syn|fr|si fait|q=archaic}}
#: {{ux|fr|Tu ne m’aimes pas, n’est-ce pas ? — '''Si''' !|t=You don’t like me, do you? — '''Yes, I do'''!}}
#: {{ux|fr|Moi, je n'ai rien fait ! — '''Si''' !|t=I didn't do anything! — '''Yes, you did'''!}}

=====Usage notes=====
The positive particle usage is uncommon in Québec, where most speakers use ''[[oui]]'' instead.
